== Events == * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1858]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In the event known as {{ill|Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|ja|廷臣八十八卿列参事件|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, officials such as {{ill|Iwakurakura Toshimi|ja|岩倉具視|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and others from the pro-【攘夷】 court, numbering 88 non-aristocratic courtiers, staged a sit-in to oppose the signing of the {{ill|Treaty of Amity and Commerce|ja|修好通商条約|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1863]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} became custodians of the {{ill|Aizu Domain|ja|会津藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and began referring to themselves as the {{ill|Mibu Rōshi-gumi|ja|壬生浪士組|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1633]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Gōkōmei Tennō|ja|後光明天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 110th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1654]]). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1708]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yuasachōzan|ja|湯浅常山|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (died [[1781]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1705]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Jinsai|ja|伊藤仁斎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (born [[1627]]). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1806]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Onogawa Kisaburō|ja|小野川喜三郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a 5th-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1758]]).
