{{Lunisolar March}}
'''March 12''' is the 12th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1858]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日}}) – In the event known as {{ill|Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|ja|廷臣八十八卿列参事件}}, officials such as {{ill|Iwakurakura Toshimi|ja|岩倉具視}} and others from the pro-【攘夷】 court, numbering 88 non-aristocratic courtiers, staged a sit-in to oppose the signing of the {{ill|Treaty of Amity and Commerce|ja|修好通商条約}}.
* {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1863]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日}}) – The {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組}} became custodians of the {{ill|Aizu Domain|ja|会津藩}} and began referring to themselves as the {{ill|Mibu Rōshi-gumi|ja|壬生浪士組}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1633]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日}}) – {{ill|Gōkōmei Tennō|ja|後光明天皇}}, the 110th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇}} (died [[1654]]).
* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1708]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日}}) – {{ill|Yuasachōzan|ja|湯浅常山}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生}}) (died [[1781]]).

== Deaths ==
