* {{ill|Bunka|ja|文久}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1806]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日}}) – {{ill|Onogawa Kisaburō|ja|小野川喜三郎}}, a 5th-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱}} (born [[1758]]).

