{{Lunisolar March|qq=}}
'''March 12''' is the 12th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1858]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|12=draft}}) – In the event known as {{ill|Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|ja|廷臣八十八卿列参事件|qq=|12=draft}}, officials such as {{ill|Iwakurakura Toshimi|ja|岩倉具視|qq=|12=draft}} and others from the pro-【攘夷】 court, numbering 88 non-aristocratic courtiers, staged a sit-in to oppose the signing of the {{ill|Treaty of Amity and Commerce|ja|修好通商条約|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1863]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|12=draft}} became custodians of the {{ill|Aizu Domain|ja|会津藩|qq=|12=draft}} and began referring to themselves as the {{ill|Mibu Rōshi-gumi|ja|壬生浪士組|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1633]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Gōkōmei Tennō|ja|後光明天皇|qq=|12=draft}}, the 110th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|12=draft}} (died [[1654]]).
* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1708]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yuasachōzan|ja|湯浅常山|qq=|12=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|12=draft}}) (died [[1781]]).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1705]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Jinsai|ja|伊藤仁斎|qq=|12=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|12=draft}}) (born [[1627]]).
* {{ill|Bunka|ja|文久|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1806]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Onogawa Kisaburō|ja|小野川喜三郎|qq=|12=draft}}, a 5th-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=|12=draft}} (born [[1758]]).

