== Births == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1633]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Gōkōmei Tennō|ja|後光明天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 110th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (died [[1654]]). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1708]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Yuasachōzan|ja|湯浅常山|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) (died [[1781]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1705]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Jinsai|ja|伊藤仁斎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) (born [[1627]]). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1806]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Onogawa Kisaburō|ja|小野川喜三郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a 5th-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (born [[1758]]).
