== Events == * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1858]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}}) – In the event known as {{ill|Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|ja|廷臣八十八卿列参事件|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|qq=}}, officials such as {{ill|Iwakurakura Toshimi|ja|岩倉具視|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwakurakura Toshimi|qq=}} and others from the pro-【攘夷】 court, numbering 88 non-aristocratic courtiers, staged a sit-in to oppose the signing of the {{ill|Treaty of Amity and Commerce|ja|修好通商条約|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Treaty of Amity and Commerce|qq=}}. * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunkyū|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1863]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 29|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinsengumi|qq=}} became custodians of the {{ill|Aizu Domain|ja|会津藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aizu Domain|qq=}} and began referring to themselves as the {{ill|Mibu Rōshi-gumi|ja|壬生浪士組|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mibu Rōshi-gumi|qq=}}.
