== Deaths == * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1705]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Itō Jinsai|ja|伊藤仁斎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itō Jinsai|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru|qq=}}) (born [[1627]]). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunka|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1806]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 30|qq=}}) – {{ill|Onogawa Kisaburō|ja|小野川喜三郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onogawa Kisaburō|qq=}}, a 5th-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokozuna|qq=}} (born [[1758]]).
