== Events == * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1858]] [[:en:April 25|April 25]]) – In the event known as {{ill|Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|ja|廷臣八十八卿列参事件|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|qq=}}, officials such as [[:en:Iwakura Tomomi|Iwakurakura Toshimi]] and others from the pro-【攘夷】 court, numbering 88 non-aristocratic courtiers, staged a sit-in to oppose the signing of the {{ill|Treaty of Amity and Commerce|ja|修好通商条約|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Treaty of Amity and Commerce|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安政五カ国条約}}. * [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunkyū]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1863]] [[:en:April 29|April 29]]) – The [[:en:Shinsengumi|Shinsengumi]] became custodians of the [[:en:Aizu Domain|Aizu Domain]] and began referring to themselves as the {{ill|Mibu Rōshi-gumi|ja|壬生浪士組|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mibu Rōshi-gumi|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 壬生浪士}}.
== Births == * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 10th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1633]] [[:en:April 20|April 20]]) – [[:en:Emperor Go-Kōmyō|Gōkōmei Tennō]], the 110th [[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor of Japan]] (died [[1654]]). * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1708]] [[:en:May 2|May 2]]) – {{ill|Yuasachōzan|ja|湯浅常山|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuasachōzan|qq=}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru|qq=}}) (died [[1781]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1705]] [[:en:April 5|April 5]]) – [[:en:Itō Jinsai|Itō Jinsai]], a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru|qq=}}) (born [[1627]]). * [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunka]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1806]] [[:en:April 30|April 30]]) – [[:en:Onogawa Kisaburō|Onogawa Kisaburō]], a 5th-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokozuna|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} (born [[1758]]).
