'''March 12''' is the 12th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|qid=Q96759840|1=tomobiki}}{{efn|ja|友引|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q9418169}}{{efn|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q9418169}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|qid=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1858|en|1858|qid=Q7684|lt=1858|1=1858}} {{ill|April 25|en|April 25|qid=Q2531|lt=April 25|1=April 25}}) – In the event known as {{ill|Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|ja|廷臣八十八卿列参事件|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teimin Hachijukkyo Ressan Jiken|1=Q11486610|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11486610}}, officials such as {{ill|Iwakura Tomomi|en|Iwakura Tomomi|qid=Q428200|lt=Iwakurakura Toshimi|1=Iwakura Tomomi}} and others from the pro-【攘夷】 court, numbering 88 non-aristocratic courtiers, staged a sit-in to oppose the signing of the {{ill|Treaty of Amity and Commerce|ja|修好通商条約|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Treaty of Amity and Commerce|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安政五カ国条約|1=Ansei Treaties|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1152499}}.
* {{ill|Bunkyū|en|Bunkyū|qid=Q730266|lt=Bunkyū|1=Bunkyū}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1863|en|1863|qid=Q7701|lt=1863|1=1863}} {{ill|April 29|en|April 29|qid=Q2535|lt=April 29|1=April 29}}) – The {{ill|Shinsengumi|en|Shinsengumi|qid=Q221031|lt=Shinsengumi|1=Shinsengumi}} became custodians of the {{ill|Aizu Domain|en|Aizu Domain|qid=Q4389944|lt=Aizu Domain|1=Aizu Domain}} and began referring to themselves as the {{ill|Mibu Rōshi-gumi|ja|壬生浪士組|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mibu Rōshi-gumi|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 壬生浪士|1=Mibu Rōshigumi|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11242196}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kan'ei|en|Kan'ei|qid=Q1192913|lt=Kan'ei|1=Kan'ei}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1633|en|1633|qid=Q6870|lt=1633|1=1633}} {{ill|April 20|en|April 20|qid=Q2524|lt=April 20|1=April 20}}) – {{ill|Emperor Go-Kōmyō|en|Emperor Go-Kōmyō|qid=Q329765|lt=Gōkōmei Tennō|1=Emperor Go-Kōmyō}}, the 110th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|en|Emperor of Japan|qid=Q208233|lt=Emperor of Japan|1=Emperor of Japan}} (died {{ill|1654|en|1654|qid=Q6970|lt=1654|1=1654}}).
* {{ill|Hōei|en|Hōei|qid=Q1145262|lt=Hōei|1=Hōei}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1708|en|1708|qid=Q6846|lt=1708|1=1708}} {{ill|May 2|en|May 2|qid=Q2545|lt=May 2|1=May 2}}) – {{ill|Yuasachōzan|ja|湯浅常山|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuasachōzan|1=Yuasa Jōzan|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q6565723}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q125199930}}) (died {{ill|1781|en|1781|qid=Q7719|lt=1781|1=1781}}).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Hōei|en|Hōei|qid=Q1145262|lt=Hōei|1=Hōei}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1705|en|1705|qid=Q6830|lt=1705|1=1705}} {{ill|April 5|en|April 5|qid=Q2507|lt=April 5|1=April 5}}) – {{ill|Itō Jinsai|en|Itō Jinsai|qid=Q640808|lt=Itō Jinsai|1=Itō Jinsai}}, a Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q125199930}}) (born {{ill|1627|en|1627|qid=Q6833|lt=1627|1=1627}}).
* {{ill|Bunkyū|en|Bunkyū|qid=Q730266|lt=Bunka|1=Bunkyū}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1806|en|1806|qid=Q6903|lt=1806|1=1806}} {{ill|April 30|en|April 30|qid=Q2536|lt=April 30|1=April 30}}) – {{ill|Onogawa Kisaburō|en|Onogawa Kisaburō|qid=Q2024560|lt=Onogawa Kisaburō|1=Onogawa Kisaburō}}, a 5th-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokozuna|comment=changed title based on wikidata|1=Yokozuna|qid=Q1067277}} (born {{ill|1758|en|1758|qid=Q7639|lt=1758|1=1758}}).

